Package: richR
Type: Package
Title: Function Enrichment analysis and Network construction
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kai", "Guo", email = "guokai8@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Junguk", "Hur", email = "junguk.hur@med.und.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides functions for functional enrichment
    analysis (ORA) via hypergeometric testing, Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA),
    and kappa-score-based term clustering. Provides publication-ready
    visualizations including bar plots, dot plots, network graphs, heatmaps,
    and cluster plots. Includes a color-enhanced UpSet plot for set intersection
    visualization.
